import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import {Playground} from 'docz'
import Notification from './Notification'
import Box from './Box'

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"notification"}}>{`Notification`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"basic-usage"}}>{`Basic usage`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={0} __code={`<Notification />`} __scope={{props,Notification,Box}}>
  <Notification />
</Playground></MDXTag>
